'''Kevin Schmitt''' is an employee for [[LucasArts]]. He was the Lead Level Designer for ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron (video game)|Star Wars: Rogue Squadron]]'', ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]]''. He also voiced [[TK8252]] in ''Mysteries of the Sith''.

He is friends with [[Ryan Kaufman (real person)|Ryan Kaufman]], who named [[Gavin Zmitt]] after him.

